    Class and Description
    Client
    The Hedera protocol wrapper for the SDK, used by all transaction and query types.
    FreezeTransaction
    Set the freezing period in which the platform will stop creating events and accepting transactions.
    Hbar
    Typesafe wrapper for values of hbar providing foolproof conversions to other denominations.

    Common units of hbar; for the most part they follow SI prefix conventions.

    HederaNetworkException
    Wrapper for all transport-related exceptions.

    HederaThrowable
    Closed set of exception types thrown by this SDK; where HederaThrowable is passed to a callback, it is one of these types: HederaStatusException HederaNetworkException MaxQueryPaymentExceededException (thrown for queries)
